  "prompt": "What is the average and highest package of Galgotia University Noida?",
  "response": "As of the latest available data, Galgotias University in Greater Noida has seen a variety of placement offers for its students. The average package typically ranges around 4-5 lakhs per annum, although this figure can vary based on the specific program and year. The highest package offered has been reported to be significantly higher, often reaching around 10-12 lakhs per annum or more, especially for students in fields like engineering and technology.\n\nPlease note that these figures can change annually based on industry demand, the economy, and the specific companies participating in campus placements. For the most current and specific data, it is advisable to contact the university's placement cell directly or visit their official website.",
